data.description: Beautifully level fully fenced horse property with CID maintained community well irrigation system. Home is serviced by its own private well.  30X36 shop/garage with exterior RV plug in. Home has had numerous updating since seller purchased including but not limited to roof, furnace, heat pump, bathrooms, windows, flooring, ceiling fans, and more!!!!
